  <brief_title>Clinical Trial to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of &quot;Theobromine Capsule&quot; as an Antitussive in Acute Cougher</brief_title>
  <official_title>Therapeutic Confirmatory Clinical Trial to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of &quot;Theobromine Capsule 300mg&quot; as an Antitussive Agent in Acute Cough Patients.</official_title>
