  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this clinical trial is to evaluate the antitussive effect of &quot;Theobromine capsule
      300mg&quot; in patients with acute bronchitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study is double blinded, randomized, parallel designed, phase III clinical trial to
      evaluate the efficacy and safety of &quot;Theobromine capsule 300mg&quot; versus &quot;Levodropropizine
      syrup&quot; in patients with acute bronchitis.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
